{"tid":2413822,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣太太認識丹麥男6天閃婚被狂酸","createTime":"2021-02-19T03:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T11:59:29.000Z","uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2da503ce8995f5845fa429e9d9d8b6661a0b9fae","tid":2413822,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mirrormedia.com.tw/assets/images/20210218190059-c30f5ec3632d347d1559308e353f77a6-mobile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.com.tw%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F20210218190059-c30f5ec3632d347d1559308e353f77a6-mobile.jpg&h=b09a7c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n異國婚姻時有所聞，不過若是交往短短6天就閃婚，應該難免會引起大家的關注。近日有對異國戀夫妻於YouTube頻道「丹麥先生X台灣太太」釋出影片，透露彼此認識短短6天就閃婚的經過，沒想到卻引起大批網友嘲諷狠酸，台灣太太昨（17）日於臉書po文反擊，強調自己用了7年的時間，讓自己從「醜小鴨變自己心中的女神」，而且也用這段時間更認識、了解自己，「當對的人一出現，可以馬上發現。」她更向看衰的網友表示，自己現在的人生很美好、很幸福。"},{"pid":"7b680b7438d458bc36b27c48bf5d4f076f6e956f","tid":2413822,"uid":118346,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"近日有對異國戀夫妻「丹麥先生X台灣太太」影片在網路上爆紅，因影片中透露2人透過交友軟體Tinder認識彼此，2人首次見面喝咖啡聊天後，第2次就約會看電影，沒想到第3次見面時2人就直接登記閃婚，前後短短交往才6天就決定步入婚姻，引起許多台灣網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n多數台灣網友都不看好這段婚姻，甚至留言狠酸嘲諷2人，「到時候發生了甚麼事記得提醒我帶爆米花回來看」「究竟會不會變成丹親媽媽呢？讓我們繼續看下去」「究竟巨人結局還是你們先結局持續追」；不過也有不少民眾獻上祝福，「雙方過得開心就好」「能相識就是緣分，正能量加油！」<br />\n<br />\n針對多數網友的冷嘲熱諷「ㄈㄈ尺、CCR女台、愛洋腸」等等，台灣太太昨於臉書po文反擊，指曾被渣男騙過、借過錢的經驗，這讓她痛定思痛，決定要好好學習兩性感情的知識，也透過7年的時間讓自己從「醜小鴨變自己心中的女神」，而且也用這段時間更認識、了解自己，「當對的人一出現，可以馬上發現。」"},{"pid":"c963e8ff2791f27f582ecb9dfed0d3e87f1aac32","tid":2413822,"uid":331739,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"丹親媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><ins></ins>"},{"pid":"3c3146e76d617422b0921d1681368c61c95bca4e","tid":2413822,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:47:50.000Z","msg":"台灣太太表示，只是這回剛好透過Tinder，找到了對方。最後她向大家表示感謝之意，「所有人生夢想都達成的開掛的人生，因為我曾經超級無敵努力。台灣太太在此，謝謝大家的關注。我要繼續找我老公撒嬌了，掰掰。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MexsgwwWa58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMexsgwwWa58&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69BvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=dbc6c838\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MexsgwwWa58</a>"},{"pid":"fafb4aa1b66049f3a9a1eeee43c6f91178fcf3cf","tid":2413822,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"洋腸"},{"pid":"6462118732099e736f9be1a127fbe5fa09c51151","tid":2413822,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:48:31.000Z","msg":"左眼見到鬼"},{"pid":"4c2ab3b48e26743538b960f86ec2f626a6aaa252","tid":2413822,"uid":81234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:50:12.000Z","msg":"鬼佬口味真係唔同D"},{"pid":"1d1a4e3e72731ed5ecaa35dd0a2efe4079589ec8","tid":2413822,"uid":106336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:52:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gah-DsoWFp0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGah-DsoWFp0&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69BvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=14414dc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gah-DsoWFp0</a>"},{"pid":"aae893b9d5eaadd25b1a22d714787c6421507284","tid":2413822,"uid":35508,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"佢就正啦<br />\n老公成個reus咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aea8a273dfb8e4e0d0c6356a49407988c782f95","tid":2413822,"uid":10438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"見面5秒就"},{"pid":"46e34cf434616f997c8c373d9a1dd41195668cbd","tid":2413822,"uid":71433,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4c2ab3b48e267435